/-- A `G`-invariant linear map induces a linear map out of the coinvariants of a
`G`-representation. -/
def lift (f : V â†’â‚—[k] W) (h : âˆ€ (x : G), f âˆ˜â‚— Ï x = f) :
    Ï.Coinvariants â†’â‚—[k] W :=
